text: Dedushkin () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Kharabali, Kharabalinsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 23 as of 2010. == Geography == It is located on the Volga River, 14 km WSW from Kharabali. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kharabalinsky District
title: Dedushkin
